{"tid":47113,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同一位陪我經歷過人生低潮既女朋友進入分手邊緣","createTime":"2016-12-20T06:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T12:01:03.000Z","uid":22739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbc7c0470da447b7bf3cb90afec07af5ca87ad5","tid":47113,"uid":22739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:22:38.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊左差唔多2年 <br />\n早大半年開始久唔久嘈交 而我脾氣不嬲都好大<br />\n之後我嘗試慢慢改過 收下d死人脾氣<br />\n但當我以爲之後都相安無事<br />\n直到早2日女朋友向我提出分手<br />\n個人真係崩潰哂 依加先識得自我反省<br />\n覺得真係忽略左好多佢既野<br />\n佢係我人生最苦既時候陪我走過 無嫌棄我<br />\n一齊搬入新居 成間屋都係大家既回憶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好內疚"},{"pid":"167f98dd182e9a8bb665fca33a4d9d170de33234","tid":47113,"uid":20630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"巴打做錯左啲咩？"},{"pid":"6acf4464f429b5571016b3445448c3a78b61e163","tid":47113,"uid":36603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:52:07.000Z","msg":"佢分手果陣講左啲咩？"},{"pid":"2d05d9437b1fa96ab9e4f326c23d298c7ee2ccb1","tid":47113,"uid":22739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打做錯左啲咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實無乜具體 可能生活上細節我忽略左佢同我脾氣又差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bfee0cdf3bf776fb7fd2f9f8f0cc52f261bde6","tid":47113,"uid":22739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢分手果陣講左啲咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢想比大家靜下 已經唔想咁想理呢段感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a863c51a750c27051069189ddd19560f33303b6","tid":47113,"uid":9711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:58:27.000Z","msg":"捉"},{"pid":"4a7b38a264b41a7ecc9a30cabaebdec8f373ecd5","tid":47113,"uid":32059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"同樓主差唔多，<br />\n<br />\n復合唔到架喇，重新振作啦"},{"pid":"d165bb0e6a63866d